Privacy Protection Addendum

By using or distributing this software, you agree to the following additional
terms:

1. Local Processing by Default: All biometric inference and signal processing
   must be performed exclusively on the local device. You must NOT transmit,
   upload, or stream user video feeds or physiological metrics to any external
   server or cloud service, UNLESS the data subject has given explicit, informed
   consent that clearly describes what data is collected, where it is sent, how
   it will be used, and how long it will be retained. Such consent must be
   freely given, specific, and revocable at any time.

2. Consent Requirement: You shall not use this Software to collect information
   or physiological data from any individual without their explicit consent.

3. No Backdoors in Distribution: If you redistribute or modify this code, you
   must maintain these strict local-processing guarantees. You are prohibited
   from modifying the software to surreptitiously collect or transmit user data.

